{"questionId":"39729166-8e92-42cc-8ed6-76acdb673a3c_11","correctAnswer":"565","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Set up","content":"Substitute $h=557.33$ into $h=\\frac{9(v-273.15)}{5}+32$ and solve for $v$: $$557.33=\\frac{9(v-273.15)}{5}+32.$$"},{"title":"Solve","content":"Subtract 32: $525.33=\\frac{9(v-273.15)}{5}$. Multiply by 5: $2626.65=9(v-273.15)$. Divide by 9: $v-273.15=291.85$. Add 273.15: $v=565$."},{"title":"Answer","content":"<strong>565</strong> is correct."}]}